flowchart TB
    subgraph MGMT[Management Plane]
        Portal[Azure Portal]
        CLI[Azure CLI]
        ARM[ARM / Bicep]
    end

    subgraph RUNTIME[Runtime Plane]
        FE[Frontend]
        Worker[Worker Instances]
        App[App Process]
    end

    subgraph SCM[SCM Plane]
        Kudu[Kudu / SCM Site]
        Zip[zipdeploy]
        Logs[Logs / Diagnostics]
    end

    Portal -->|configure| FE
    CLI -->|configure| Worker
    ARM -->|declare desired state| Worker

    FE --> Worker
    Worker --> App

    Kudu -->|deploy| Worker
    Kudu --> Zip
    Kudu --> Logs

    MGMT -. settings changes may trigger restart .-> RUNTIME
    SCM -. separate endpoint / tooling .-> RUNTIME
